  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0d86 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0dbd\u0dd3\u0da7\u0dbb\u0dca 3900\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3900 liters of fuel brought from India seized",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The security forces of the north have discovered that the smuggling of fuel has been carried out by the smugglers from India to the northern coast by sea and selling it at high prices.",
        "The Mulankavil Police said that a suspect was arrested with 3600 liters of kerosene suspected to be brought by sea from India in the Nachchikuda area of \u200b\u200bMulankavil Police Area, Kilinochchi.",
        "Also, a suspect was arrested with 300 liters of diesel hidden in a house in Jaffna city during a search conducted by the Jaffna Police, which was carried out according to information received by the Army Intelligence Division.",
        "The police point out that the traffickers have planned to sell kerosene and diesel for between 600 and 1000 rupees per liter and its value is over 30 lakh rupees.",
        "The arrested suspects are residents of Nachchikuda and Jaffna and the police have taken steps to refer them to the courts.",
        "Due to the severe shortage of fuel, there is a risk of smugglers bringing fuel from India and selling it at high prices, so the Navy is also taking steps to strengthen the security of the North."
      ],
